```mermaid
flowchart TD
    %% Project Detection
    Workspace["Workspace Root Path"] --> Hash["Stable Hash\n(project_id)"]
    Hash --> Session["OpenCode Session"]
    
    %% Memory Operations
    Session --> SaveMem["saveMemory()\nwith project_id"]
    Session --> Recall["contextRecall\nproject-scoped"]
    Session --> Search["searchMemories()\nproject-scoped"]
    
    %% Scoped Recall
    Recall --> Query["SELECT * FROM memories\nWHERE project_id = $1\nORDER BY importance DESC"]
    Query -->|Current Project| Results["Project Memories"]
    Query -->|Legacy Fallback| Legacy["NULL project_id\n(high importance)"]
    
    %% Search Modes
    Search --> Mode{"searchMode"}
    Mode -->|project| ProjQ["WHERE project_id = $1"]
    Mode -->|legacy| LegQ["WHERE project_id IS NULL"]
    Mode -->|global| GlobQ["No project filter"]
    
    %% Database
    subgraph DB["PostgreSQL"]
        ProjQ --> Memories["memories table\n+ project_id index"]
        LegQ --> Memories
        GlobQ --> Memories
        SaveMem --> Memories
    end
    
    %% Legacy Preservation
    Legacy -.->|Preserved, not deleted| Memories
    
    style Session fill:#e8f5e9
    style Memories fill:#fff3e0
    style Legacy fill:#fce4ec
```